data.description: Come see this spectacular low maintenance patio home in River Run! This property backs to the Poudre River Trail and comes with added privacy from neighboring homes. Lawn care and snow removal taken care of by the HOA. Premium finishes throughout. Granite countertops, wood floors, and more. Two bedrooms and laundry on the main floor. The garden level finished basement allows for additional living, entertaining, and storage. A 5-minute drive to grocery, shopping, and dining. Schedule your showing today and come see it in person!
